{
  "stem": "9701.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the proverb is [LATIN SPEECH,] which, in translation, means not in school, but in life, you learn.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were many others that he taught me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But this one, for some reason, really stands out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I used to write it on the flyleaf of all my books, probably much to the dismay of my teachers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember being told by one of the Jewish children that I'm not a good Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked, you know, what does it mean to be a good Jew?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why am I not a good Jew?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember my parents explaining to me that there's no such thing as a good Jew, or a bad Jew, or a good Christian, or a bad Christian.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there-- there's such a thing as a good human being that has certain moral and ethical values.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what I should adhere to and strive for.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It bothered me that my parents were different, that I was different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I went to someone else's home, in some ways, I wanted to be-- I wanted my family to be the way that family was, the, the way those children were.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the same time, I felt great discomfort.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their value system seemed to be different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- it's difficult for me to describe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- I guess the, the value system that my par-- or the, the standard of life that my parents had-- the, you know, the, the music, the books, the art-- it wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it bothered me that it wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I wanted to be back home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I was back home, I wished I could be-- or my parents could be the way the others were.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
